This directory will hold per-model findings files for the end-of-full-wave audit.

Expected files (created during the audit, not before):
  - gemini-findings.md  — produced by Gemini independently (must NOT see opus-findings.md)
  - opus-findings.md    — produced by Opus independently (must NOT see gemini-findings.md)

See AGENTS.md section 6 for the multi-model audit pattern.
